00:10:55.290 --> 00:10:58.509
Now this thing, of course,
is again as always,

00:10:58.509 --> 00:10:59.800
the effective degradation rate.

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:03.440
So it's the sum of the sort
of physical degradation rate,

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:06.570
plus this dilution
due to growth.

00:11:06.570 --> 00:11:09.170
But in general, the
true degradation,

00:11:09.170 --> 00:11:11.920
the physical degradation is much
faster than the cell division

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:12.980
rate.

00:11:12.980 --> 00:11:15.350
So this is very close
to actually just

00:11:15.350 --> 00:11:18.140
the physical degradation rate.

00:11:18.140 --> 00:11:22.640
But in any case, it's
